review_data.title: Nice patio seating, quiet atmosphere
review_data.content: Restaurant Medina is located in Wollishofen and can be accessed with public transit, Tram #7 (Morgental or Butzenstrasse). Medina has a very nice sunny patio seating area (with umbrellas) at the front and on the main street and is very popular during the warmer months....More
